				<li id="16738936" class="cmnt-root" data="41" data-d="1658124939000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=110969" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">Sujiren99</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578949/Academy-Glintstone-Staff" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">18 Jul 2022 02:15</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16738936" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">I would say this staff is among top 3 for intelligence builds, and depending on the build could be the best one.<br/><br/>In terms of raw damage, Lusats is always going to be the best, at least until extremely high levels, where Prince of Death&apos;s staff will eventually outscale it. However, it has the drawback of consuming a lot more FP for each cast, meaning you will also need a lot of mind to use Lusat&apos;s<br/><br/>Regal Scepter is slightly weaker than Lusats, but does not consume additional FP, so it&apos;s considered to be the most practical endgame staff for high intelligence build. Do note, that Regal Scepter&apos;s scaling seems to be mostly backloaded, kinda like with Erdtree seal, meaning that it gets a lot of additional scaling from 60-80 intelligence.<br/><br/>Academy Glintstone staff has the best scaling up until 68 intelligence, where Regal Scepter finally catches up to it and starts surpassing it.<br/><br/>On short  Academy Glintstone &gt; 68 Intelligence <br/>Regal Scepter scepter 68 intelligence and above.<br/>Lusat&apos;s only if you have high int and mind.<br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16738936" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16738936" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>41</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16738936"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16738936" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16738936"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
