				<li id="16436660" class="cmnt-root" data="100" data-d="1646246536000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=123909" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">arbiterofwhim</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578949/Academy-Glintstone-Staff" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">02 Mar 2022 13:42</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16436660" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Ok I did some testing and gathered some values for the Academy Glintstone Staff to compare against the Meteorite Staff. TL;DR the AG Staff is worse than the Meteorite Staff until +14.<br/><br/>Academy Glintstone Staff: (at INT 28)<br/>+0 Sorc Scaling = 130<br/>Glintstone Pebble on Troll leg = 130 damage<br/>+1 Sorc Scaling = 132<br/>+2 Sorc Scaling = 134<br/>+3 Sorc Scaling = 137<br/>+4 Sorc Scaling = 139<br/>+5 Sorc Scaling = 142<br/>+6 Sorc Scaling = 144<br/>+7 Sorc Scaling = 146<br/>+8 Sorc Scaling = 149 (INT scaling increases to A)<br/>+9 Sorc Scaling = 151<br/>+10 Sorc Scaling = 154<br/>+11 Sorc Scaling = 156<br/>+12 Sorc Scaling = 159 (INT scaling increases to S)<br/>+13 Sorc Scaling = 161<br/>+14 Sorc Scaling = 163 (STR scaling increases to D)<br/>Glintstone Pebble on Troll leg = 174 damage<br/>+15 Sorc Scaling = 166<br/>+16 Sorc Scaling = 168<br/><br/>For comparison the Meteorite Staff (at INT 28):<br/>Sorc Scaling = 163<br/>Glintstone Pebble on Troll leg = 173 damage</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data